              "content": "you are a helpful, intelligent website scraping assistant ",
              "role": "model"
            },
            {
              "content": "=\nYou're provided a Markdown scrape of a website page.  \nYour task: provide a two-paragraph of what this page is about.  \n\nRules:  \n- Your extract should be comprehensive—similar level of detail as a published paper.  \n- Use a straightforward, spartan tone of voice.  \n- If it's empty, just say. \n",
              "role": "model"
            },
